reviews.text:
Very very good food
Taste so good in all dishes
Highly recommend the Man Cheong Chicken,
Fried Noodle with Soya Sauce, A pot of soup of the day, Braised lotus roots with pork belly cubes in salty bean cured sauce

Service ok
Seats are bit tight

Toilet can be better

Very good food even serve you in very late late night, very late Supper
The chicken and goose are of my favorite. Fresh and nicely done.  Around $500 for two.

食晚飯。
